msgid ""
"A URL prefix must end with <b>://</b> (e.g. <code>chrome://</code>) or "
"<b>:</b> (e.g. <code>about:</code>).<br><br>Entered: <code>{p}</code>"
msgstr ""
"Un prefijo de URL debe terminar con <b>://</b> (ej. "
"<code>chrome://</code>) o <b>:</b> (ej. "
"<code>about:</code>).<br><br>Introducido: <code>{p}</code>"

